cs.CL, cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR 

This paper deals with the task of image caption generation, which involves both computer vision and natural language processing. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.CL (Computation and Language) and cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses the use of neural networks, which falls under cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper involves information retrieval, which is related to cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
